WEATHER SUMMARY
A LOW 970 JUST NE OF SCOTLAND IS MOV E AND COLD AIR WITH WINTRY SHWRS IS
MOV DOWN OVER THE FAROES FM NW.
FCST FOR THE SEA-BANKS SURROUNDING THE FAROE ISLANDS - VALID 24 HRS:
